snippet.title: Update 8.0 | Rise of the Warlords Highlights
snippet.description:
Play Warframe now! Sign up for Warframe *Open Beta* @ www.warframe.com/signup
Warframe Producer Dave Kudirka goes over Update 8 with us, he covers everything from new environments,mods, weapons and, of course, the Dojo.

NOTE: Warframe is now in Open Beta- apologies for the video typo!
